{
  "stem": "16930.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 410.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister left-- left Vienna on the transport in the beginning of August.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's sort of-- it wasn't-- it was a separation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't a separation, because we'll pick you up in a couple of months, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it's sort of like-- you follow?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a goodbye and then you'll see them a couple months later.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the-- that was the plan.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the hope.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what they told us, so we didn't really see it as a separation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know anybody on-- on this particular kindertransport.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had seen-- maybe seen one or two people before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But looking out on the train station, I saw another kid whom I'd gone to class with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I talked to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I waved to him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And subsequent-- and he also showed up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He-- so he-- I don't know what happened to him, but I saw him on the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had also plans for going on-- on the transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I don't know whether he-- since I was the last transport, I don't know what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took a long time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only a matter of the railroad station going from there to Holland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because of the troop movements, which were-- the-- the war started on the 1st of September '39 with Poland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a considerable amount of troop movement, so what would have been a turn maybe of 10, 12 hours perhaps, or less, took a couple of days, because they were shunting our train to a side while they let the troop trains go ahead.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we went to Le Havre, France, a port.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we took the ferry across to England, to Dover, England.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "N.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
